Dialogue: 3,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风险是生活的调味品
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Risk is the spice of life.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.04,0:00:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.04,0:00:38.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我问你
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度有几个大公牛？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How many big bulls are there in India?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有两个，你和我
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only two. You and I.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.16,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，我们是天生一对
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.16,0:00:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, we are made for each other.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有了现在的地位，是因为我们冒了风险
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We've reached where we are, because we took risks.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.88,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.88,0:00:56.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:58.00,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这很简单
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.00,0:00:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, it's very simple.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只要以 Grindlays 的名义签发支票就行了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just have to issue cheques in the name of Grindlays.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对你来说只是一个即期交易
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's just a ready-forward deal for you.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.80,0:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.80,0:01:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.04,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.04,0:01:10.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I would need...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}作为回报，我们会从 Grindlays 那里拿到收据
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...BRs from Grindlays in return.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会得到的，绝对会
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you will get them. Definitely.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.36,0:01:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交给我吧
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.36,0:01:17.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.32,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只需要15天
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.32,0:01:19.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's just a matter of 15 days.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在15天内，NHB 将会拿回资金
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And in 15 days, NHB will get its money back.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，德里的提议仍然有效
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Sir, the Delhi offer stands.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.04,0:01:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是哈沙德向你保证的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.04,0:01:31.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's Harshad's guarantee to you, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会在议会中占有一席之地
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will get positioned in the parliament.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“好吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Okay. I'll do it.'
