Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果出了什么差错
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if anything goes wrong...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:04.96,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.96,0:02:05.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我付出四十年心血
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...my reputation of forty years...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}打造的名声
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...for which I worked so hard...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 都将化为乌有
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...will go down the drain.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你明白吗?-先生
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Do you understand that? - Sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当消息从上面传来的时候你
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you thinking of going down...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么要往坏的方面想？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when the messages are coming from up?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们受到上帝的保护
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are protected by higher powers.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早上好，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，马德文，请进
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Yes, Madhavan. Please come in.'
Dialogue: 3,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你看到那份文件了吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'So... Did you see the file?'
Dialogue: 3,0:03:35.64,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.64,0:03:36.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这需要时间来消化
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It will take time to comprehend.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是个金融骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a financial scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要用不同的方式来调查
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We will need to investigate it differently.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这是大盗的新称呼
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, it's a new word for a big theft.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I get that.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是金融欺诈
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a financial fraud.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交易是很复杂的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Transactions are very complicated.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，如果我们深究细节，我们会陷入一个数字的网络中
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, if we go into details, we will get caught in a web of numbers.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，我想说的是，让我们专注于我们所知道的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I'm saying, let's just focus on what we know.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是盗窃
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a theft.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查小偷只有一个办法，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And there is only one way to investigate thieves, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmm.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}照你的方法做，不要有任何压力
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do it your way. There won't be any pressure.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，记住一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, remember one thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个骗局比博福斯大50倍
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This scam is 50 times bigger than Bofors.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且可能比博福斯更加黑暗
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It can be murkier than Bofors.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}另外，政府和媒体..
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Plus, the Government and the media...
