Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, what's new in that?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.80,0:04:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经习惯了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.80,0:04:27.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are used to that.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我几天时间，先生，让我把队伍集合起来
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give me a few days, sir, to get my team together.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行行长？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI Governor?
