Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- We have to investigate him? -[laughs]
Dialogue: 3,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果由你决定，你甚至会调查我
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If it were up to you, you would even investigate me.
