Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'Did you catch hold of a James Bond this time?'
Dialogue: 3,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又一个神秘人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Another mystery-man.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个詹姆斯 · 邦德住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And does this James Bond live here?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是詹姆斯 · 邦德，是苏伯拉曼尼亚姆
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not James Bond. Subramaniam.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，你不觉得这是个陷阱吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, don't you think this can be some sort of a trap?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会设计陷害我? 哈沙德？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who will try to trap me? Harshad?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心，他不是电影里的反派角色
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't worry. He isn't a villain from a movie.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何，如果我现在发生了什么事..
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway, if anything happens to me now...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公众会立刻对他产生怀疑
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...public's perception will immediately doubt him.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是一个聪明的古吉拉特人，他不会这么愚蠢
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is a smart Gujarati. He won't be so stupid.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，这个神秘的邦德从哪里打来的电话？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, where did this mystery Bond call from?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公共电话
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Public booth.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧我们都同意哈沙德是个聪明的古吉拉特人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. Let's agree that Harshad is a smart Gujarati.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是因为他，很多愚蠢的人变得焦虑
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But because of him, a lot of stupid people are getting anxious.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是个500亿的骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, it's a 5,000 crore scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 涉及到很多人-我知道
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- A lot of people are involved. - I know.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 从上到下-Sucheta 女士
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- From top to the bottom. - Sucheta madam.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哦 你好?-是的，跟我来
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Oh, Subramaniam? - Yes, follow me.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请过来
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please come.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小心点，夫人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Be careful, madam.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请进，请坐
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please come. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在议会反对派的巨大压力下..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Under immense pressure from the opposition in the parliament...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府终于决定采取更果断的措施
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the government has finally decided to take more decisive steps...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查金融诈骗案
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to investigate the financial scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 震撼了孟买证券交易所”
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...that has rocked the Bombay Stock Exchange."
Dialogue: 3,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“印度央行还宣布... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"The RBI has also announced..."
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.52,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 成立委员会，由副... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.52,0:06:32.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...that it has formed a committee headed by Deputy..."
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查局什么都不懂
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI won't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只会找替罪羊
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They will only look for a scapegoat.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而印度储备银行... ... 为了挽救自己的形象，会让他们玷污其他所有人的形象
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And RBI... to save its image, RBI will let them tarnish everyone else's.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我就知道
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I knew it.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道他们都会背叛我们
Dialogue: 2,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I knew they would all betray us.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这正是我所担心的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just what I was afraid of.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德，我们得做点什么否则..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, we need to do something, or else...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你在听我说话吗?-我听到了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Are you listening to me? - I heard you.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只相信我的妻子和苏伯拉曼尼亚姆
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...trust only my wife and Subramaniam.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是为什么我要在这儿见你，在他家
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why I'm meeting you here, at his house.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，就菲尔瓦尼而言..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, as far as Pherwani is concerned...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}恐怕..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我自己也做不了什么
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I can't do much myself.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么你不能？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why can't you do much?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么要告诉我们这些？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you telling us this?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是印度储备银行的行长
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are the Governor of RBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想的话，你可以直接和菲尔瓦尼谈
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can talk to Pherwani directly if you want.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.88,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼不是一个三流的经纪人，也不是像哈沙德那样的暴发户
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.88,0:07:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pherwani is not a small-time broker or an upstart like Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他名声在外
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has a reputation.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能直接和他对质
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't confront him directly.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 看
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Look. -[clears throat]
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管怎么说，我有自己的局限性
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All said and done, I have my limitations.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是公职人员
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm a government servant.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果 RBI 真的想..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If RBI really wants to...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 采取行动对付像菲尔瓦尼这样的人，那么..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...take action against people like Pherwani, then...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}应该有外部压力
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...there should be external pressure.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你... 明白了吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You... get it, don't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mean...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们要建立舆论压力？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we have to build external pressure?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But how?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有任何实质性的证据
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without any substantial proof or verification.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}国家住房银行给了格林德莱50亿..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}NHB gave 500 crores to Grindlays...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德就是这样拿到钱的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So that Harshad could have access to the cash.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有他们需要在账簿中展示的东西..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All that they needed to show in their books...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是一个简单的即时交易
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...was a simple ready-forward transaction.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为没有来自格林德莱的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because there were no securities from Grindlays.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:44.44,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是哈尔沙德如何向印度国家银行偿还资金的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.44,0:08:48.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that is how Harshad managed to repay the cash to SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:49.76,0:08:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你就是新闻出版社500亿报道的消息来源吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.76,0:08:53.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, you were the source of News Press' 5,000 crore story?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚安
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good night.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哈沙德-你好，费尔瓦尼先生
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad. - Yes, Pherwani ji.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道发生了什么，对吧
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'You know what's happened. Right?'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么这么担心? 你的名字不会出来的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you so worried? 'Your name won't come out.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI 的问题已经解决了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, the SBI problem has been solved.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不欠 SBI 一分钱
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't owe a single penny to SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]“放松点，不会有事的”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Just relax. Nothing is going to happen.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德，苏切塔打电话给我
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, Sucheta had called me.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁? 苏切塔 · 达拉尔？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who? Sucheta Dalal?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:41.20,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Pherwani ]‘是的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.20,0:09:41.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Yes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 她说什么?-她问..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What did she say? - She was asking...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}国家住房银行是不是给了哈沙德50亿
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if NHB gave 500 crores to Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}问我是不是与此事有关
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I bailed you out?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what did you say?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，他们要我出席委员会
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, they have asked me to appear before a committee that...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行刚刚成立了 Janakiraman 委员会
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...RBI has just formed. Janakiraman Committee.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你打算怎么跟委员会说？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what are you going to tell the committee?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好! 菲尔瓦尼先生！
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello! Pherwani ji!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论我们喜欢与否
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}♪Whether we like it or not...♪
Dialogue: 3,0:10:34.28,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是旅伴
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.28,0:10:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}♪...we are fellow travellers...♪
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.04,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在生命的道路上
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.04,0:10:43.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}♪...on the path of life...♪
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give me a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天 Sensex 指数再次崩溃... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today the Sensex crashed once again...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 在关于菲尔瓦尼先生的报道出来之后..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...after the reports came out about Manohar Pherwani...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}国家住房银行现任非执行董事长
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the current non-executive chairman of the National Housing Bank...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关于他参与骗局的事
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...regarding his involvement in the scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}各方都要求..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There have been demands from various quarters...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼先生辞职
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Mr. Pherwani resigns from his position.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}观众应该知道，国家住房银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Viewers should know that the National Housing Bank...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是印度储备银行的全资子公司
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is a wholly owned subsidiary of the RBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行行长 Venkitarajan 先生说..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The RBI governor, Mr. Venkitarajan has said...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行正在进行调查
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that RBI is looking into the charges...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快就会采取适当的措施
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and would take appropriate steps soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在说什么，费尔瓦尼先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you saying, Pherwani ji?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}辞职不是解决办法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Resignation is not a solution.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么要辞职？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why do you need to resign?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只需要说你和这笔交易没有任何关系
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just have to say that you have nothing to do with this transaction.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.24,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.24,0:11:27.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就是我的问题了，对吧? 我会处理的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then it's my problem, right? I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至于用我的名字开支票..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And as far as issuing the cheque in my name is concerned...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是我第一次这么做了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...this is not the first time I am doing this.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是货币市场的标准做法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is standard practice in the money-market.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它可能是非官方的，但每个人都这么做
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It may be unofficial, but everyone does it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦我买了这些证券，钱就会转到我的账户上
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once I buy the securities, the money will be transferred to my account.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毕竟，我是那个偿还债务的人
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After all, I'm the one who has to repay it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:50.00,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这难道不合逻辑吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.00,0:11:50.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it logical?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都这样做是为了节省时间
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone does it to save time.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会尽快归还 NHB 的50亿
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I'm returning NHB's 500 crores, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不用担心
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的名誉会得到100% 的澄清
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your name will be cleared, 100 percent.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.12,0:12:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}相信我
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.12,0:12:04.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just trust me.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}信任仍然是非常昂贵的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Trust is still something that's very expensive.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我决定了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have decided.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我别无选择..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have no other option...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只能辞职
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but to resign.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:47.12,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早上好
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.12,0:12:47.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Good morning.'
Dialogue: 3,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 马诺哈尔，j · 菲尔瓦尼先生-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Manohar. J. Pherwani ji. -[Pherwani] 'Yes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}K. 马达文 调查局联合主任
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}K. Madhavan. Joint Director, CBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有你家的搜查令
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have a warrant to search your entire house.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Carry on.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早上好
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道高尔夫球中最重要的一杆..
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know the most important shot in golf...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}永远是下一杆
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is always the next one.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的下一杆是哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And my next shot, will be on Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最重要的一个
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The most important one.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只希望他穿着得体
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just hope he is dressed appropriately.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托，他只是个业余爱好者
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on. He is an amateur.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不知道挥动板球棒和高尔夫球杆的区别
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He doesn't know the difference between swinging a cricket bat and a golf club.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他认为自己可以改变市场
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he thought he could swing the markets.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个板球运动员不会带着球棒来高尔夫球场吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This cricketer won't come to the golf course with his bat, will he?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我还是不明白
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他为什么要来高尔夫球场见你？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why is he coming to the golf course to meet you?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他绝望了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is desperate.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即将溺水的人紧紧抓住一根稻草
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A drowning man clutching at a straw.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 还有一个-好的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- There's another one. - Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有必要的话
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When it's needed...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ... 你甚至给驴子加冕-[凯迪亚笑]
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...you even crown the donkey. -[Kedia laughs]
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[哈沙德]“没错”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'That's right.'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}完美的说法
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.92,0:13:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The perfect saying.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有一个
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's yet another one.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在喀布尔，你不仅能得到豌豆，还能得到驴子
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In Kabul, you don't get only peas, you also get donkeys.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.04,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你拿到了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.04,0:13:58.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you get it?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早上好，八木
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good morning, Tyagu.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了! 你今天心情不错！
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Great! You are in a good mood today!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多么荣幸啊，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What an absolute privilege, Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The big bull.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}证交所的阿米塔布·巴沙坎
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Amitabh Bachchan of BSE.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们肯定做了什么善事 AK..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We must have done something right, AK...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们今天有机会
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that today...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}见到你
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we got an opportunity to meet you.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你会玩吗?-我? 不，谢谢..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Will you play? - Who me? No thanks...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个游戏我玩不来
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This game is beyond me.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只能用棍子玩棒击木片游戏
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can only play tipcat with a stick.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们继续
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You guys carry on.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉纳夫 · 巴伊
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav Bhai.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}加油，兄弟！
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go peel them, brother!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没问题，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's clean, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}弗瓦尼先生，你为什么不和我们一起走呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Pherwani, why don't you come with us?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说现在？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mean, right now?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我是说现在
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. I mean right now.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在这里不太舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not very comfortable here.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我在自己的办公室，喝着茶
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, if I get my space, my tea...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许我能问出正确的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I'll perhaps be able to ask the right questions.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后，也许..
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then, maybe...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会从你那里得到正确的答案
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll get the right answers from you.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmm?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我将以我的报价买下他所有的财产
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll buy all his holdings at my price.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大打折扣
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At a heavy discount.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这会杀了他的
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- It will finish him off. -[Kedia clicks tongue]
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托，再想想
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on. Think again.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你不买他的股份..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you don't buy his holdings...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他连五亿卢比都还不了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he won't have 500 crores to pay back NHB.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他将被彻底终结
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He will be completely finished. History.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，请... 请把诱惑放在一边
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, please... Please put the temptation aside.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, AK.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这样一个大骗局之后，没有人进监狱
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After committing such a big fraud, no one goes to jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:20.76,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个月后保释
Dialogue: 2,0:16:20.76,0:16:21.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bail in a month...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后，一切都被遗忘了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then, it's all forgotten.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是诱惑
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is not temptation.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的建议对生意有好处
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What I'm suggesting is good for business.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这不是生意上的事，八木
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, but this is not about business, Tyagu.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是私人恩怨
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is personal.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你别进来，先生！
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not you, Sir!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}带他走楼梯
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take him by the stairs.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样你就能参观调查局的办公室了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That way, you will get a tour of the CBI office. Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你去带他
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You come in. Bring him with you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不多，只有五层
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not much. Only five floors.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们来谈谈生意吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Shall we talk business?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我你出多少钱买我的140亿股份？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me what's your offer for my 1400 crores of holdings?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}百分之三十五
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thirty-five percent.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个该死的..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This f**...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他嗑药了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is he high?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}百分之三十五的折扣？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thirty-five percent haircut?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使在最糟糕的时候..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even in the worst of times...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 一个好的商人打折也不会超过百分之二十五
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a good businessman doesn't take a haircut of more than 25 percent.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可能不知道，但这是一个固定的市场惯例
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You may not know it, but this is a set market practice.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你误会我了，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are misunderstanding me, Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会给你35% 的折扣
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not offering you 35 percent haircut.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给你35% 的股份
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm offering you 35 percent of your entire holdings.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}14亿卢比的35% 
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thirty-five percent of 1400 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}总共是... 多少... 49亿？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Comes to... what... 490 crores?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}既然你是来和我打高尔夫的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And since you've come here to play golf with me...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会给你一个大概的数字
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I'll make it a round figure.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再加一亿，总共50亿
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take ten crores more. 500 crores in all.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你今天就能拿到
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You'll get it today.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道这就是你所需要的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know that's all you need.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.56,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Tyagi ]“今天晚上所有的股票都可以交易”
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.56,0:18:21.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] 'All the shares can be exchanged by the evening today.'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧，接受这个提议
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on. Take the offer.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么近，那么远
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So close, yet so far.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有食谱，水牛来做饭
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without a recipe, the buffalo sits down to cook.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看..
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个不懂商业的人不应该做这种事
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a person who doesn't understand business shouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他毁了所有人的生活
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He ruins it for everyone.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，让水牛自己来处理它的角吧
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, let the buffalo handle its own horns.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢你的慷慨提议
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you for your generous offer.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想让我淹死，我会把你也拖下水
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you want me to drown, I'll take you down with me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:10.96,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我一直在试图解释，但你不愿意理解
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.96,0:19:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've been trying to explain, but you're not willing to understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只想听你想听的
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You only want to hear what suits you.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 再试一次-看
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Try again. - Look.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个简单的即期交易
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This was a simple ready-forward deal.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.96,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.96,0:19:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们从格林莱斯银行那里获得了证券
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We took securities from Grindlays.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们付给格林莱斯银行50亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we paid Grindlays 500 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎么知道当时哈沙德 · 梅塔的情况？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how would I know Harshad Mehta's condition at the time?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果格林莱斯银行把钱给了哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if Grindlays gave that money to Harshad...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这怎么是我的错? 和我有什么关系？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how is that my fault? Why do I affect it?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 你说得太对了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... You are absolutely right.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是想知道..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just want to know...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你收到的那50亿证券在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...where are those securities of 500 crores that you received?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是证券，是 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not securities. BRs.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你刚才不是说..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didn't you say just now...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你从格林莱斯银行购买了价值50亿的证券？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you bought securities worth 500 crores from Grindlays Bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你刚才不是说了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just said that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在你说，这不是证券，而是 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now you are saying, it's not securities, but BRs.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是不是把我当成傻瓜了，你个傻瓜？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you take me for an a*****e, you d**k h**d! Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两个小时了，你一直在循环，试图迷惑我..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For two hours, you've been on a loop, trying to confuse me...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ BR，远期交易 ”“ BR，远期交易 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...'BR, ready-forward...' 'BR, ready-forward...'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁来给我解释一下 BR 是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who will explain to me? What is a BR?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BR 到底是什么? 你能告诉我吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What the hell is a BR? Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，BR 的意思是银行收据
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, BR means bank receipt.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他说的对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is he right?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说”银行收据”有那么难吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, was it so hard for you to say "bank receipt"?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BR……BR……BR
Dialogue: 2,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BR... BR...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会再见的，这次谈话结束了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll see you again. This congregation is over.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会在同一个地方问你同样的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I'm going to ask you the same questions at the same place.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下次喝茶前告诉我真相
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And next time, tell me the truth before having tea.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别再用你们市场的语言
Dialogue: 2,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not in the language of your market.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用一种我这样的穷人能听懂的语言，好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In a language that a poor man like me can understand. Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你现在可以走了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'You may go now.'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出去的时候乘电梯
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take the lift on your way out.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}接下来有你忙活的
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You did all the hard work coming up.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在..
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:08.48,0:21:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管你是搭电梯还是爬楼梯
Dialogue: 2,0:21:08.48,0:21:09.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...whether you take the lift or the stairs...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唯一的路就是向下
Dialogue: 2,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the only way, is down.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我还有一句谚语给你们
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I also have a proverb for you.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大脑更强大，还是公牛更强大？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is the brain mightier, or the bull?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，你会说是公牛，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course, you'd say the bull, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你已经忘了如何使用你的大脑
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...because you've forgotten how to use your brain.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则，你就不会炫耀球技并抛出箴言给他..
Dialogue: 2,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or else, you wouldn't have shown off and thrown proverbs at him...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后不做任何交易就离开了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and walked away without a deal...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你最好快点找到买家
Dialogue: 2,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You'd better find a buyer fast.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:32.76,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些调查局的家伙都疯了，他们无所不能
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.76,0:21:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These CBI guys are crazy. They can do anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们甚至可以扇你耳光
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They can even slap you.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:49.48,0:21:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是个骄傲的人
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.48,0:21:50.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is a proud man.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.04,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还需要一些时间
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.04,0:21:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It will take some time.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.48,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，只需要再一次盘问
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.48,0:21:53.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But sir, just one more session...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会毫不犹豫地招供
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and he will confess without a second thought.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的自尊心受到了伤害
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is a man whose pride has been wounded.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像他这样的人会睡不着觉
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People like him can't sleep.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不会花太多时间的
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He won't take much time.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那之前先把注意力集中在哈尔沙德 · 梅塔先生身上
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Till then, let's focus on Mr. Harshad Mehta, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他得到的时间越多..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The more time he gets...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就会找到自救的方法
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he will find a way to save himself.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:15.28,0:22:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，马德文，记住，他是个聪明的家伙
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.28,0:22:18.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, Madhavan, remember. He is a smart chap.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:19.04,0:22:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小心对待他
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.04,0:22:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Be careful with him.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:20.96,0:22:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“他有一些非常有权势的朋友在保护他”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.96,0:22:22.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'He has some very powerful people protecting him.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.04,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.04,0:22:23.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.96,0:22:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[达斯]“在逮捕他之前，一定不要留下任何漏洞”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.96,0:22:26.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Make sure you leave no loopholes before bringing him to book.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.08,0:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.08,0:22:28.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等我们把他带回来，先生，就永远不会有事了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When we bring him in, sir, it will be for good.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会占用你太多时间
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I won't take much of your time.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只有一个小问题
Dialogue: 2,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just have one little question.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是投资管理部门的负责人
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are in charge of treasury and investment management division.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.44,0:22:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的...-对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.44,0:22:56.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes... - Right?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，但你不知道你的下属..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right. And yet, you weren't aware that your subordinates...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:00.76,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和哈萨德合谋进行这样的掠夺？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:00.76,0:23:02.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...were in cahoots with Harshad in such a plunder?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.76,0:23:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你看...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.76,0:23:07.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You see... - [Khemani clears throat]
Dialogue: 3,0:23:09.72,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的工作是为我的老板争取最好的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.72,0:23:13.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My job is to get the best deal for my employer, SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 没错-就是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Right. - That's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:16.48,0:23:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}执行实际交易是西塔拉曼的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.48,0:23:20.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's Sitaraman's job to execute the actual transactions.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 那是他的工作-好吧..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- That was his job. - Okay...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:23.48,0:23:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.48,0:23:24.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能为他的失误负责，你知道
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I can't be responsible for his botch-ups, you know.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.08,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.08,0:23:28.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.84,0:23:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他告诉我..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.84,0:23:29.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If he tells me...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他已经收到了证券
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that he has received the delivery of securities...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.60,0:23:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.60,0:23:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then what can I do?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-没错-我信任他
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Correct. - I trusted him.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他撒谎了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he lied.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:40.32,0:23:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:23:40.32,0:23:41.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:43.00,0:23:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你信任他？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.00,0:23:43.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You trusted him?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:44.04,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的-好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.04,0:23:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes. - Okay...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他撒谎了-当然
Dialogue: 2,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- And he lied. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在我明白了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now I understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道，我有很多下属..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know, Mr. Khemani, I have many subordinates...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不得不依靠他们的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and I have to rely on their work.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的-我真的信任他们
Dialogue: 2,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes. - And I really trust them. Really trust them.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果我的下属..
Dialogue: 2,0:24:02.24,0:24:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if any of my subordinates...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:04.60,0:24:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}会做出这样的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.60,0:24:06.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...would have done such a plunder...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:07.84,0:24:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会狠狠地扇他一巴掌，让他尿裤子
Dialogue: 2,0:24:07.84,0:24:10.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I would've slapped him so hard that he would pee in his pants.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.08,0:24:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但也许你的工作不允许你使用暴力
Dialogue: 2,0:24:12.08,0:24:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But then maybe your job does not allow you to be violent.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，其实不是
Dialogue: 2,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah. It doesn't actually.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:21.68,0:24:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的工作..
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.68,0:24:22.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My job...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我变得暴力
Dialogue: 2,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...allows me to be violent.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:27.24,0:24:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时候
Dialogue: 2,0:24:27.24,0:24:28.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:31.08,0:24:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有一件事我想知道
Dialogue: 2,0:24:31.08,0:24:32.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just one thing I want to know.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说，我很好奇，仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, I'm curious. That's all.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.36,0:24:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你真的想控制西塔拉曼..
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.36,0:24:39.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, if you really wanted to exercise control over Sitaraman...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:39.84,0:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你本可以做到的，对吧
Dialogue: 2,0:24:39.84,0:24:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] '...you could have done it. Right?'
Dialogue: 3,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“是还是不是? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Yes or no?'
Dialogue: 3,0:24:43.96,0:24:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是不是？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.96,0:24:46.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes or no, Mr. Khemani?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要回答是或不是
Dialogue: 2,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just a yes or a no.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:50.40,0:24:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在我的船舱里会更舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:24:50.40,0:24:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll be more comfortable in my cabin...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:52.08,0:24:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么? 大声点，我听不见
Dialogue: 2,0:24:52.08,0:24:53.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What? Louder. I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:54.24,0:24:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的下属都看着呢
Dialogue: 2,0:24:54.24,0:24:55.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My staff is watching.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:55.80,0:24:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大声点... 请大声点
Dialogue: 2,0:24:55.80,0:24:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Louder... Louder, please.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:58.72,0:25:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别人在看着我们
Dialogue: 2,0:24:58.72,0:25:00.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Staff is looking at us.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:01.80,0:25:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在看什么? 做你的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:25:01.80,0:25:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you looking at? Do your work.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:03.76,0:25:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我是说... 我在那儿会更舒服-是啊，走吧
Dialogue: 2,0:25:03.76,0:25:06.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I mean... I'll be comfortable there. - Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:07.12,0:25:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 来吧，我们走-拜托，抱歉
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.12,0:25:08.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Come on, let's go. - Please. Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:10.48,0:25:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你相信我，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:10.48,0:25:11.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You trust me, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:11.60,0:25:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的... 当然-来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:25:11.60,0:25:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes... Absolutely. - Come.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:14.08,0:25:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的柜子看起来更像巴比 · 拉希里的，而不是你的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.08,0:25:16.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your locker looks more like Bappi Lahiri's than yours.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:16.60,0:25:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么多珠宝
Dialogue: 2,0:25:16.60,0:25:18.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So much jewellery.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:18.64,0:25:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我女儿要结婚了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:18.64,0:25:22.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Actually, my daughter is getting married. That's why.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:23.12,0:25:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么把你女儿牵扯进来，可怜的父亲？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:23.12,0:25:25.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why drag your daughter into this, my poor father?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:26.60,0:25:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使是在婚礼上，你是怎么得到这么多珠宝的？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:26.60,0:25:29.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even for the wedding, how did you get so much jewellery?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:30.24,0:25:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我女儿用她的钱买的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:30.24,0:25:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My daughter bought it with her money.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.28,0:25:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好吧，她的钱-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:33.28,0:25:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay. Her money. - Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:35.08,0:25:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你女儿叫什么名字?-安妮塔
Dialogue: 2,0:25:35.08,0:25:36.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What's your daughter's name? - Anita.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:36.96,0:25:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}安妮塔
Dialogue: 2,0:25:36.96,0:25:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anitha.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:38.68,0:25:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}安妮塔有个"T"
Dialogue: 2,0:25:38.68,0:25:40.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anita with a "T".
Dialogue: 3,0:25:40.08,0:25:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 安妮塔，好的-谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.08,0:25:41.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Anita. Okay. - "Ta".
Dialogue: 3,0:25:42.08,0:25:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她是做什么的？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:42.08,0:25:43.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What does she do?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:43.52,0:25:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:25:43.52,0:25:44.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:25:44.88,0:25:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一定是一份好工作，毕竟有这么多珠宝
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.88,0:25:47.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It must be a good job. So much jewellery, after all.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:48.68,0:25:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:48.68,0:25:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:50.64,0:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她可以挣钱买那么多的珠宝
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.64,0:25:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}She can earn and buy so much jewellery.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:52.00,0:25:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但她不能有自己的储物柜？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:52.00,0:25:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But she can't have her own locker?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:56.84,0:25:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“奇怪”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:56.84,0:25:57.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Strange.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:58.52,0:26:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“事情是这样的，卡玛特先生... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:58.52,0:26:00.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The thing is, Mr. Kamat...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:00.24,0:26:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须封锁这个柜子
Dialogue: 2,0:26:00.24,0:26:02.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we will have to seal the locker.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 先生!-不幸的是
Dialogue: 2,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Kamat] 'Sir!' - Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:04.96,0:26:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，婚礼还有几天就要举行了，你不能封锁这个柜子
Dialogue: 2,0:26:04.96,0:26:07.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the wedding is in a few days. You can't seal the locker.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:07.44,0:26:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:26:07.44,0:26:08.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:08.72,0:26:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，你已经封住了你的嘴..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.72,0:26:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, you have sealed your mouth...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:10.96,0:26:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以我们还需要密封一些东西，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:10.96,0:26:12.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...so we also need to seal something, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:12.96,0:26:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 否则我们就跟不上节奏了-先生
Dialogue: 2,0:26:12.96,0:26:14.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Or we will be left behind. - Sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:14.92,0:26:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有一个建议
Dialogue: 2,0:26:14.92,0:26:15.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One more advice.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:16.76,0:26:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该担心的不是储物柜，而是锁起来的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:26:16.76,0:26:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Instead of the locker, you should worry about the lock-up.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:19.48,0:26:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ‘先生’-听着，如果你被捕了..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:19.48,0:26:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Kamat] 'Sir.' - Look, if you get arrested...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:22.44,0:26:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会在婚礼上送走你的女儿？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:22.44,0:26:24.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who will give away your daughter at the wedding?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:25.52,0:26:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很忙
Dialogue: 2,0:26:25.52,0:26:26.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I am very busy.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:26.80,0:26:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，求你了先生，先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:26.80,0:26:28.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, please sir. Sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:28.68,0:26:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 恭喜你女儿-先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.68,0:26:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Congratulations for the wedding. - Sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:30.96,0:26:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}祝你今天过得愉快
Dialogue: 2,0:26:30.96,0:26:31.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a good day.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:34.48,0:26:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.48,0:26:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.64,0:26:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“在和所有这些人谈过之后... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.64,0:26:37.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'After talking to all these people...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:37.92,0:26:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 我开始感到... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:37.92,0:26:39.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...I've begun to feel...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:39.52,0:26:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你才是 SBI 真正的老板
Dialogue: 2,0:26:39.52,0:26:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you are the real boss of SBI.
