Dialogue: 2,0:26:42.96,0:26:45.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI. Sitaraman Bank of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:46.40,0:26:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:46.40,0:26:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:47.56,0:26:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我什么都没做
Dialogue: 2,0:26:47.56,0:26:49.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:51.56,0:26:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你所有的上级都说是你干的
Dialogue: 2,0:26:51.56,0:26:53.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All your seniors are saying that you did it.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:53.92,0:26:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都在用你的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:26:53.92,0:26:55.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is taking your name.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:57.60,0:26:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是贵宾，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:57.60,0:26:58.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are a VIP, aren't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:00.64,0:27:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你乘飞机去 Palani
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.64,0:27:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You travel by air to Palani.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:02.72,0:27:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是不是？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.72,0:27:03.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you or not?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:09.52,0:27:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道，先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:09.52,0:27:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know, sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:11.96,0:27:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 先生...-嘿! 你不会印地语吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:11.96,0:27:14.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Senior... - Hey! Don't you know Hindi?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:15.76,0:27:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 泰米尔-泰米尔...-我来自德里，明白了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:15.76,0:27:18.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Tamil-Tamil... - I'm from Delhi. Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:20.12,0:27:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用印地语说
Dialogue: 2,0:27:20.12,0:27:21.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Speak in Hindi.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:23.40,0:27:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有上级的授权我又能做什么呢，先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:23.40,0:27:26.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can happen without the authority of the seniors, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:27.64,0:27:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说没有上级的批准什么都不会发生
Dialogue: 2,0:27:27.64,0:27:30.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You say nothing happens without the approval of the seniors.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:30.92,0:27:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高年级学生说他们什么都不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:27:30.92,0:27:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Seniors say they don't know anything...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:32.40,0:27:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}都是小孩子闯的祸
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.40,0:27:33.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...it's all the junior's doing.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:35.32,0:27:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.32,0:27:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What should I do?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:39.08,0:27:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}锡塔拉曼小姐，我对银行业的技术细节没有兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.08,0:27:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sitaraman ji, I have no interest in banking technicalities.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:43.24,0:27:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只想知道名字
Dialogue: 2,0:27:43.24,0:27:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just want to know the name.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:47.04,0:27:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我所有参与者的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:27:47.04,0:27:50.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, tell me the names of all those who are involved.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:51.24,0:27:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则，在今天这个时代..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:51.24,0:27:53.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Otherwise, in today's day and age...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:53.72,0:27:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你将接受火刑的考验
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.72,0:27:56.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you will have to take a trial by fire.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:56.12,0:27:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:56.12,0:27:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:01.04,0:28:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想想吧
Dialogue: 2,0:28:01.04,0:28:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Think about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:03.68,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高年级的学生将不会受到惩罚
Dialogue: 2,0:28:03.68,0:28:05.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Seniors will go scott-free.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:07.08,0:28:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而你会被爆菊的
Dialogue: 2,0:28:07.08,0:28:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will be f**ked.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:10.80,0:28:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:10.80,0:28:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, do you know?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:15.88,0:28:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,0:28:15.88,0:28:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:17.36,0:28:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局，今天冻结..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:17.36,0:28:19.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Central Bureau of Investigation, today froze...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:19.88,0:28:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票经纪人哈尔沙德·梅塔的银行账户
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.88,0:28:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...stock broker, Harshad Mehta's bank accounts.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:21.96,0:28:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“所有这些都是对他... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:21.96,0:28:23.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"All of this is a part of the investigation..."
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.04,0:28:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 调查的一部分 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:24.04,0:28:25.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...being conducted against him..."
Dialogue: 3,0:28:25.64,0:28:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 因欺诈挪用印度国家银行的”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:25.64,0:28:29.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...for fraudulently misappropriating rupees 500 crores..."
Dialogue: 3,0:28:29.12,0:28:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 50亿卢比”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:29.12,0:28:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...from the State Bank of India."
Dialogue: 3,0:28:36.92,0:28:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一切都毁了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.92,0:28:38.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everything is ruined.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:39.52,0:28:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局开始调查了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:39.52,0:28:40.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The curse of CBI has struck.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:41.96,0:28:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们所有的银行账户都被冻结了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.96,0:28:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All our bank accounts are frozen.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:45.88,0:28:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你现在能应付吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:45.88,0:28:46.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Will you manage now?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:48.24,0:28:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:28:48.24,0:28:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:49.88,0:28:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去吧，孩子们，上楼去
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.88,0:28:51.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on, kids. Go upstairs. Go on.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:59.08,0:29:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 告诉我-你想听什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:59.08,0:29:00.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Tell me. - What do you want to hear?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:01.92,0:29:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“啊? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:01.92,0:29:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Huh?'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:04.24,0:29:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解决方案？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:04.24,0:29:04.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Solution?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:07.36,0:29:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和我一样拥有这家公司，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:07.36,0:29:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You own this company as much as I do. Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:09.68,0:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要总是问我怎么办，自己也动动脑子
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.68,0:29:11.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't always ask questions. Come with a solution sometimes.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:11.76,0:29:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我动脑子的时候，你总是高高在上
Dialogue: 2,0:29:11.76,0:29:14.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When I came with a solution, you were flying high.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:15.64,0:29:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“阿什温，一切交给我吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:15.64,0:29:17.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Ashwin, I'll manage everything."
Dialogue: 3,0:29:20.36,0:29:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果费尔瓦尼对中央调查局开口
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.36,0:29:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If Pherwani shoots off his mouth to the CBI, Harshad...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.52,0:29:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样? 坐下
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.52,0:29:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So? So what? Sit down.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:25.96,0:29:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}动动脑子
Dialogue: 2,0:29:25.96,0:29:27.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Use your brain sometimes.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:28.52,0:29:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果费尔瓦尼说了什么，PMO也跑不了，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.52,0:29:31.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If Pherwani says anything, the PMO will also be mentioned. Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:33.12,0:29:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:33.12,0:29:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:35.04,0:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我们只是在聊天-让他们听听
Dialogue: 2,0:29:35.04,0:29:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Ashwin] 'We are just talking.' -[Harshad] 'Let them hear.'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:37.12,0:29:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在孩子们面前大喊大叫
Dialogue: 2,0:29:37.12,0:29:38.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You were yelling in front of the kids.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:39.24,0:29:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在大家都知道了，请坐吧，嫂子
Dialogue: 2,0:29:39.24,0:29:41.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone knows now. Have a seat, Bhabhi.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:41.48,0:29:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}坐这儿
Dialogue: 2,0:29:41.48,0:29:42.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sit here.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:50.28,0:29:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你明白你在说什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:50.28,0:29:52.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, do you understand what you are saying?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:53.84,0:29:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为中央调查局会对总理办公室下手吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:53.84,0:29:56.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think the CBI will go after the Prime Minister Office?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:01.40,0:30:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有... 对这个费尔瓦尼做点什么吧
Dialogue: 2,0:30:01.40,0:30:03.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And... do something about this Pherwani.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:05.64,0:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他开口..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:05.64,0:30:07.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If he opens his mouth...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:11.16,0:30:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们走
Dialogue: 2,0:30:11.16,0:30:12.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's go.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:23.08,0:30:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个该死的麦德文！
Dialogue: 2,0:30:23.08,0:30:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This bloody Madhavan!
Dialogue: 3,0:30:27.08,0:30:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他对我政治迫害
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.08,0:30:28.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's on a witch hunt.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:30.52,0:30:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟他讲道理... 我是说..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:30.52,0:30:31.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Reasoning with him... I mean...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:33.92,0:30:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根本没用
Dialogue: 2,0:30:33.92,0:30:34.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's impossible.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:35.92,0:30:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只是想要一个战利品
Dialogue: 2,0:30:35.92,0:30:38.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All they are looking for is trophy heads...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:39.16,0:30:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}陈列在他的橱柜里
Dialogue: 2,0:30:39.16,0:30:41.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to display in their cabinets.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:42.84,0:30:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很抱歉
Dialogue: 2,0:30:42.84,0:30:43.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:46.76,0:30:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但如果把钱还回去...-别说了，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:30:46.76,0:30:48.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But if returning the money will... -[Pherwani] 'Stop it, Harshad.'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一遍一遍地说把钱还上
Dialogue: 2,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are repeating the same s**t again and again and again.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:51.08,0:30:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们都知道钱不会很快到位
Dialogue: 2,0:30:51.08,0:30:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We both know the money is not coming anytime soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，求你闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 2,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, for f**k's sake. Shut up.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:00.96,0:31:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:00.96,0:31:01.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:04.04,0:31:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查组
Dialogue: 2,0:31:04.04,0:31:04.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when Janakiraman...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:06.28,0:31:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}将提交
Dialogue: 2,0:31:06.28,0:31:07.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...will file...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:08.52,0:31:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}初步报告
Dialogue: 2,0:31:08.52,0:31:10.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...his primary report...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:13.08,0:31:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些中央调查局的混蛋..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:13.08,0:31:15.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Those bastards from CBI...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:17.72,0:31:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会再来找我的
Dialogue: 2,0:31:17.72,0:31:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They will come again, for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:20.44,0:31:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我知道”
Dialogue: 2,0:31:20.44,0:31:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'I know.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:22.92,0:31:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:22.92,0:31:23.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:24.56,0:31:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能再接受审问了
Dialogue: 2,0:31:24.56,0:31:27.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...won't be able to handle another interrogation.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:32.64,0:31:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的德里之梦毁了一切
Dialogue: 2,0:31:32.64,0:31:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My dream of Delhi has ruined everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:38.16,0:31:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我，我该怎么办?
Dialogue: 2,0:31:38.16,0:31:39.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Tell me Swami ji, what should I do? -[swami] 'Hari Om!'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:40.20,0:31:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阁下，告诉我，我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:40.20,0:31:42.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Hari Om, Swami ji. Tell me. What do I do?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:42.48,0:31:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}障碍是生活不可或缺的一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:31:42.48,0:31:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Obstacles are part and parcel of life.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:45.04,0:31:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只要坚持信念
Dialogue: 2,0:31:45.04,0:31:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just keep the faith.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:46.44,0:31:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎样才能坚持信念？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:46.44,0:31:48.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can I keep the faith?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:49.16,0:31:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说过中央调查局什么都不会做的
Dialogue: 2,0:31:49.16,0:31:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You said the CBI won't do anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:51.72,0:31:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们冻结了我所有的账户，锁定了所有的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:31:51.72,0:31:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They've froze all my accounts and locked everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:54.52,0:31:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间是打开每一把锁的钥匙
Dialogue: 2,0:31:54.52,0:31:57.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Time has the key to every lock.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:58.16,0:31:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有的门都会再次为你打开
Dialogue: 2,0:31:58.16,0:31:59.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[swami] 'All doors will be open for you again.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:59.96,0:32:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“现在... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:31:59.96,0:32:01.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'In this current situation...'
Dialogue: 3,0:32:02.20,0:32:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让中央调查局做好自己的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:32:02.20,0:32:03.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...let CBI do its work.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:04.08,0:32:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去他妈的
Dialogue: 2,0:32:04.08,0:32:05.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}F***...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:06.20,0:32:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阁下，我会死的
Dialogue: 2,0:32:06.20,0:32:07.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Swami ji, I'll be doomed.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:09.40,0:32:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果迈德文再审问菲尔瓦尼
Dialogue: 2,0:32:09.40,0:32:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If Madhavan interrogates Pherwani again...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:11.00,0:32:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会坦白一切
Dialogue: 2,0:32:11.00,0:32:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he will confess to anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:13.40,0:32:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们控制了菲尔瓦尼的思想
Dialogue: 2,0:32:13.40,0:32:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have control over Pherwani's mind.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:16.16,0:32:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请放心
Dialogue: 2,0:32:16.16,0:32:17.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[swami] 'Be assured.'
Dialogue: 3,0:32:22.76,0:32:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该死的白痴！
Dialogue: 2,0:32:22.76,0:32:25.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}F*****g idiot!
Dialogue: 3,0:32:48.68,0:32:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}爸爸
Dialogue: 2,0:32:48.68,0:32:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Papa.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:52.36,0:32:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}妈妈！
Dialogue: 2,0:32:52.36,0:32:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mom!
Dialogue: 3,0:33:02.80,0:33:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-喂-恭喜
Dialogue: 2,0:33:02.80,0:33:04.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:05.16,0:33:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:05.16,0:33:07.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What for?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:07.40,0:33:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼死了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:07.40,0:33:08.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pherwani is dead.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:47.92,0:33:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看见费尔瓦尼了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:47.92,0:33:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you seen Pherwani?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:49.92,0:33:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是个健康的人
Dialogue: 2,0:33:49.92,0:33:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He was a fit guy.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:52.12,0:33:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他以前像个职业运动员一样
Dialogue: 2,0:33:52.12,0:33:55.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, every day on Marine Drive, without fail...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:55.32,0:33:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每天在海滨大道上慢跑，风雨无阻
Dialogue: 2,0:33:55.32,0:33:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he used to jog like a pro-athlete.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:57.80,0:34:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像他这样的人会得心脏病吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:57.80,0:34:00.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can a person like him suffer a heart attack?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:02.12,0:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想他成了他自己的刽子手
Dialogue: 2,0:34:02.12,0:34:03.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think he became his own hangman.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:04.80,0:34:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[拉吉迪普]“这些天来，你们所有人和中央调查局... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:04.80,0:34:06.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rajdeep] 'For all these days, you all and the CBI...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:07.08,0:34:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ...逼高了他的血压”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:07.08,0:34:08.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...pushed up his blood pressure.'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Kiran ]“我甚至听说这是自杀”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Kiran] 'I even heard that it was suicide.'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:17.96,0:34:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你怎么看，苏切塔? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:17.96,0:34:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'What do you think, Sucheta?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:19.52,0:34:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ 费尔瓦尼，自杀还是自然死亡? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:19.52,0:34:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Pherwani. Suicide or natural death?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:23.68,0:34:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 苏切塔?-什么事？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:23.68,0:34:24.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 'Sucheta?' - Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:25.16,0:34:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ 费尔瓦尼，自杀还是自然死亡? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:25.16,0:34:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Pherwani. Suicide or natural death?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:30.96,0:34:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还好吗
Dialogue: 2,0:34:30.96,0:34:31.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Are you okay?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:33.60,0:34:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:33.60,0:34:34.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Yeah?'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:35.28,0:34:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:34:35.28,0:34:36.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All right.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:50.96,0:34:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是我人生中第二次明白
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.96,0:34:53.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For the second time in life, I've understood something.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:54.72,0:34:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忧虑是通往火葬场的必经之路
Dialogue: 2,0:34:54.72,0:34:56.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Worrying is a sure path to your pyre'.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:19.36,0:35:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我带了披萨回来
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.36,0:35:21.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've brought pizza from Open House.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.08,0:35:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来，我们吃饭吧
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.08,0:35:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:28.76,0:35:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:28.76,0:35:29.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:30.84,0:35:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:30.84,0:35:31.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:36.76,0:35:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:36.76,0:35:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:39.80,0:35:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:39.80,0:35:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:43.12,0:35:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想是我杀了费尔瓦尼
Dialogue: 2,0:35:43.12,0:35:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Sucheta crying] - I think I killed Pherwani.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:01.88,0:36:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}费尔瓦尼是我们的主要证人..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:01.88,0:36:03.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pherwani was our prime witness...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:04.16,0:36:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在他永远都不会开口了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:04.16,0:36:06.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and now he is permanently quiet. Finished.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:08.40,0:36:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“嗯”
Dialogue: 2,0:36:08.40,0:36:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Hmm.'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:11.04,0:36:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:11.04,0:36:12.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Do you think...'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:13.12,0:36:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ...这是... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:36:13.12,0:36:14.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...it was...'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:14.96,0:36:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么看，先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:14.96,0:36:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you think, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:16.88,0:36:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当地警方显然会说是心脏病发作
Dialogue: 2,0:36:16.88,0:36:18.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Local police will obviously say it's heart attack.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:18.56,0:36:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们想假装这是自然死亡
Dialogue: 2,0:36:18.56,0:36:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They want to pretend it was a natural death.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:20.52,0:36:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你知道，我也知道
Dialogue: 2,0:36:20.52,0:36:21.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you know it and I know it.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:22.24,0:36:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太巧合了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:22.24,0:36:23.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's too much of a coincidence.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:27.20,0:36:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果不是谋杀那么..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:27.20,0:36:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If it wasn't murder then...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:29.32,0:36:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们肯定是把他引向了自杀
Dialogue: 2,0:36:29.32,0:36:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they definitely led him to suicide.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:32.32,0:36:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我们只是在浪费时间，先生，我们必须行动
Dialogue: 2,0:36:32.32,0:36:35.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, we are just wasting time, sir. We have to move.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:37.80,0:36:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我看了委员会发表的第一份报告
Dialogue: 2,0:36:37.80,0:36:40.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have read the first report that Janakiraman committee has published.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:41.56,0:36:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续
Dialogue: 2,0:36:41.56,0:36:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:43.16,0:36:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们登记一个案件，反对腐败的印度国家银行官员..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:43.16,0:36:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's register a case against the corrupt SBI officials...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:45.56,0:36:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}越快越好
Dialogue: 2,0:36:45.56,0:36:46.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:46.96,0:36:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后，让我们进入斗牛场
Dialogue: 2,0:36:46.96,0:36:48.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then, let's enter the bullfight.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:50.12,0:36:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是我们的斗牛士
Dialogue: 2,0:36:50.12,0:36:51.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will be our Matador.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:10.76,0:37:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没人听到门铃响吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:10.76,0:37:12.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Doesn't anyone hear the doorbell?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:21.92,0:37:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}惊喜！
Dialogue: 2,0:37:21.92,0:37:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Surprise!
Dialogue: 3,0:37:23.68,0:37:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.68,0:37:24.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:25.68,0:37:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是迈德文
Dialogue: 2,0:37:25.68,0:37:27.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}K. Madhavan.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:28.72,0:37:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}终于
Dialogue: 2,0:37:28.72,0:37:29.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Finally...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:30.76,0:37:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和你见面了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:30.76,0:37:31.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I get to see you.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:32.84,0:37:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 我不是粉丝
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.84,0:37:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... not a fan.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:35.40,0:37:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是你的信徒
Dialogue: 2,0:37:35.40,0:37:37.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm your devotee, My Lord. A devotee.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:37.88,0:37:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以和你握手吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:37.88,0:37:40.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can I shake hands with you? Please?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:40.96,0:37:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我手有点脏
Dialogue: 2,0:37:40.96,0:37:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A little...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:44.76,0:37:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很高兴见到你
