Dialogue: 2,0:41:39.88,0:41:41.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can take some home-cooked food.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:41.84,0:41:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，嫂子，我们需要得到许可
Dialogue: 2,0:41:41.84,0:41:44.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, Bhabhi, we need to take permission for that.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:45.04,0:41:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得我们都不应该去那里
Dialogue: 2,0:41:45.04,0:41:48.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't think any of us should go there.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:49.36,0:41:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他们在拘留期间殴打他们呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:49.36,0:41:52.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if they hit them in custody?
Dialogue: 3,0:41:52.04,0:41:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，不，不会的？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:52.04,0:41:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, no. How can they touch them?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:08.08,0:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家好，我是印度时报的苏切塔 · 达拉尔
Dialogue: 2,0:42:08.08,0:42:10.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello, I'm Sucheta Dalal from Times of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:10.96,0:42:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们能进来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:10.96,0:42:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can we come in?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:12.60,0:42:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗨，我是苏切塔 · 达拉尔，这是德巴西 · 巴苏
Dialogue: 2,0:42:12.60,0:42:16.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hi, I'm Sucheta Dalal. This is Debashis Basu. And...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:16.24,0:42:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔 · 达拉尔
Dialogue: 2,0:42:16.24,0:42:17.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta Dalal.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:18.48,0:42:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是那个记者
Dialogue: 2,0:42:18.48,0:42:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are the one...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:19.72,0:42:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局为什么要逮捕他？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:19.72,0:42:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What reason did CBI give for the arrest?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:23.64,0:42:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你难道不知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.64,0:42:25.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Jyoti] 'Don't you know, madam. Huh?'
Dialogue: 3,0:42:27.16,0:42:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该更清楚
Dialogue: 2,0:42:27.16,0:42:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You should know.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:29.08,0:42:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你什么都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:42:29.08,0:42:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because you know everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:31.40,0:42:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是你写的文章引发了这一切吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:31.40,0:42:34.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Aren't you the one who wrote the articles that started all this?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:35.28,0:42:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔太太，我对他没有个人仇恨
Dialogue: 2,0:42:35.28,0:42:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, Mrs. Mehta. I have no personal animosity towards him.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:38.68,0:42:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是个记者，我想报道真相
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.68,0:42:41.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm just a journalist. And I wanted to report the truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:41.16,0:42:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上我们来到这里..
Dialogue: 2,0:42:41.16,0:42:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Facts. And we came here...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:43.56,0:42:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是想听听你的说法
Dialogue: 2,0:42:43.56,0:42:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...because we wanted to get your side of the story.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:45.60,0:42:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你明白的，不是吗?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:45.60,0:42:47.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You understand, don't you? -[Jyoti clicks tongue]
Dialogue: 3,0:42:47.88,0:42:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我什么都不明白
Dialogue: 2,0:42:47.88,0:42:49.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:50.28,0:42:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不明白..
Dialogue: 2,0:42:50.28,0:42:51.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't understand...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:51.72,0:42:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局怎么能把阿什温和哈尔沙德从家里带走？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:51.72,0:42:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how CBI can just take Ashwin Bhai and Harshad from home?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:55.48,0:42:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}后来，我们才知道他们被捕了
Dialogue: 2,0:42:55.48,0:42:57.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Later, we come to know that they've been arrested.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:58.32,0:42:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不明白..
Dialogue: 2,0:42:58.32,0:42:59.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't understand...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:59.92,0:43:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我们国家，这么多的恐怖分子..
Dialogue: 2,0:42:59.92,0:43:02.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that in our country, so many terrorists...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:02.28,0:43:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}罪犯和腐败的领导人到处游荡
Dialogue: 2,0:43:02.28,0:43:04.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...criminals and corrupt leaders are roaming about freely...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:05.04,0:43:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但中央调查局不去逮捕他们，为什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:05.04,0:43:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but CBI won't arrest them. Why?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:07.68,0:43:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为哈沙德对这个国家是个威胁
Dialogue: 2,0:43:07.68,0:43:09.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because Harshad is a threat to the country.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:10.32,0:43:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:10.32,0:43:11.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:11.24,0:43:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一定也是这么想的
Dialogue: 2,0:43:11.24,0:43:12.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You must be thinking this too.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:13.20,0:43:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也不明白..
Dialogue: 2,0:43:13.20,0:43:14.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I also don't understand...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:15.08,0:43:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出了问题
Dialogue: 2,0:43:15.08,0:43:17.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...agreed, there's been a problem...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:18.36,0:43:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来调查一下
Dialogue: 2,0:43:18.36,0:43:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Investigate it.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:19.96,0:43:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁在阻止你？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:19.96,0:43:21.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who is stopping you?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:21.84,0:43:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[乔蒂]“我们就在这里”
Dialogue: 2,0:43:21.84,0:43:23.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Jyoti] 'We will be right here.'
Dialogue: 3,0:43:24.64,0:43:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这房子
Dialogue: 2,0:43:24.64,0:43:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this house.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:26.76,0:43:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看住在这里的人们
Dialogue: 2,0:43:26.76,0:43:28.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at the people living here.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:29.04,0:43:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是国家的威胁吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:29.04,0:43:30.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are we a threat to the country?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:31.56,0:43:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女士，一个男人的故事对你来说比他本人更重要
Dialogue: 2,0:43:31.56,0:43:34.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Madam, a man's story is more important to you, than the man himself.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:35.44,0:43:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是事实
Dialogue: 2,0:43:35.44,0:43:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's the fact.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:50.00,0:43:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好
Dialogue: 2,0:43:50.00,0:43:50.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:54.36,0:43:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你跟我说这个干吗? 把电话放下
Dialogue: 2,0:43:54.36,0:43:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you telling me? Put the phone down.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:58.36,0:43:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:58.36,0:43:59.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:01.08,0:44:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德被捕了
Dialogue: 2,0:44:01.08,0:44:02.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad's been arrested.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:03.88,0:44:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:03.88,0:44:04.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:05.16,0:44:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:05.16,0:44:05.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, what?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:07.04,0:44:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他告诉我股价会上涨
Dialogue: 2,0:44:07.04,0:44:08.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He told me that the market will rise.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:09.48,0:44:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我借钱去投资，现在被套牢了
Dialogue: 2,0:44:09.48,0:44:12.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I borrowed money on interest. Now I am stuck.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:13.72,0:44:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当人们知道哈沙德被捕的那一刻..
Dialogue: 2,0:44:13.72,0:44:15.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The moment people come to know that Harshad has been arrested...
Dialogue: 3,0:44:15.88,0:44:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会来这里缠着我们要债
Dialogue: 2,0:44:15.88,0:44:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they will come here, pestering us to return their money.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:19.64,0:44:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们到哪里去弄钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:19.64,0:44:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where will we get the money?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:21.24,0:45:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是小偷
Dialogue: 2,0:45:21.24,0:45:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Crowd] 'There is a cry everywhere, that Harshad Mehta is the thief.'
Dialogue: 3,0:45:24.88,0:45:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是小偷
Dialogue: 2,0:45:24.88,0:45:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'There is a cry everywhere, that Harshad Mehta is the thief.'
Dialogue: 3,0:45:27.80,0:45:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是小偷
Dialogue: 2,0:45:27.80,0:45:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'There is a cry everywhere, that Harshad Mehta is the thief.'
Dialogue: 3,0:46:17.68,0:46:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，你觉得我们的办公室怎么样
Dialogue: 2,0:46:17.68,0:46:19.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Mr. Mehta, how do you like our office?'
Dialogue: 3,0:46:21.76,0:46:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有15000平方英尺，你一定觉得很小
Dialogue: 2,0:46:21.76,0:46:24.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not 15,000 square feet. Must feel small to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:27.48,0:46:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很热，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:27.48,0:46:28.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:29.76,0:46:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要我打开风扇吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:29.76,0:46:30.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Should I switch on the fan?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:32.32,0:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我得叫个电工来
Dialogue: 2,0:46:32.32,0:46:33.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll have to call an electrician.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:35.04,0:46:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那之前，深呼吸
Dialogue: 2,0:46:35.04,0:46:36.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Till then, take deep breaths.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:38.68,0:46:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从你的嘴里呼气，会让你冷静下来
Dialogue: 2,0:46:38.68,0:46:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Exhale from your mouth. It will cool you down.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:40.92,0:46:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很有效的
Dialogue: 2,0:46:40.92,0:46:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It works.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:43.16,0:46:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在学校上课的时候就是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:46:43.16,0:46:45.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We had the same problem in the school where I studied.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:46.24,0:46:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那里有风扇，但没有电
Dialogue: 2,0:46:46.24,0:46:47.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There were fans, but no electricity.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:48.40,0:46:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我就是这样通过深呼吸度过七年级的
Dialogue: 2,0:46:48.40,0:46:51.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is how I passed the seventh grade. By taking deep breaths.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:51.76,0:46:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的
Dialogue: 2,0:46:51.76,0:46:52.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Really.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:55.60,0:46:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:46:55.60,0:46:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget it.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:56.84,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们从头开始
Dialogue: 2,0:46:56.84,0:46:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:01.00,0:47:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:01.00,0:47:01.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:03.40,0:47:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}意思是你什么时候开始
Dialogue: 2,0:47:03.40,0:47:07.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning, when and how did you...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:08.32,0:47:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如何有计划地从印度国家银行偷钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:08.32,0:47:12.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...systematically steal from the State Bank of India?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:13.28,0:47:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说吧
Dialogue: 2,0:47:13.28,0:47:13.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:18.68,0:47:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我，我们有的是时间
Dialogue: 2,0:47:18.68,0:47:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me. We have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:20.80,0:47:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说吧，告诉我细节
Dialogue: 2,0:47:20.80,0:47:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on. Tell me in detail.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:26.92,0:47:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要保持沉默多久，梅塔先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:26.92,0:47:28.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How long will you stay mum, Mr. Mehta?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:31.36,0:47:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}西塔拉曼把一切都告诉我了
Dialogue: 2,0:47:31.36,0:47:32.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sitaraman has told me everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:34.24,0:47:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以我建议你..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:34.24,0:47:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why I advise you...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:35.88,0:47:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说出真相
Dialogue: 2,0:47:35.88,0:47:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:38.40,0:47:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:38.40,0:47:39.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Otherwise...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:40.28,0:47:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在你家吃了什么?炸饼
Dialogue: 2,0:47:40.28,0:47:42.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What did I have at your house? Gathia.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:44.40,0:47:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会把你的脸揍成炸饼
Dialogue: 2,0:47:44.40,0:47:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll turn your b***s into gathia.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:48.24,0:47:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:48.24,0:47:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:50.28,0:47:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，我请求你双手合十..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:50.28,0:47:52.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'So, I request you with folded hands...'
Dialogue: 3,0:47:53.00,0:47:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:47:53.00,0:47:54.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to tell me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:47:54.48,0:47:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是怎么处理从印度国家银行抢来的钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:54.48,0:47:57.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What did you do with the money you looted from State Bank of India?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:59.56,0:48:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有抢劫任何钱
Dialogue: 2,0:47:59.56,0:48:00.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I haven't looted any money.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:03.20,0:48:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经把所有的钱都还上了
Dialogue: 2,0:48:03.20,0:48:04.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've paid back everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:05.84,0:48:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:48:05.84,0:48:06.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:07.20,0:48:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是从哪里得到这笔钱来偿还的？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:07.20,0:48:09.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And from where did you get the money to repay it?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:12.92,0:48:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一定是从什么地方来的？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:12.92,0:48:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It must have come from somewhere?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:15.20,0:48:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拆了东墙补西墙
Dialogue: 2,0:48:15.20,0:48:18.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One theft to hide another... then another, to hide that one...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:20.36,0:48:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你已经偷了这么多东西，要把它们全部找出来还需要时间
Dialogue: 2,0:48:20.36,0:48:22.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've made so many thefts, it will take time to uncover all of them.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:23.56,0:48:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“在那之前... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:48:23.56,0:48:24.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Till then...'
Dialogue: 3,0:48:25.44,0:48:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就住在这里吧
Dialogue: 2,0:48:25.44,0:48:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...be our guest.'
Dialogue: 3,0:49:11.12,0:49:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德没有得到保释
Dialogue: 2,0:49:11.12,0:49:12.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad didn't get bail.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:14.96,0:49:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:14.96,0:49:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:17.32,0:49:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们说想进一步调查他
Dialogue: 2,0:49:17.32,0:49:18.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They said that they want to investigate him further.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:20.16,0:49:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们调查完你了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:20.16,0:49:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are they done investigating you?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:23.88,0:49:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德是现在唯一被拘留的人
Dialogue: 2,0:49:23.88,0:49:25.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is the only one in custody now.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:40.92,0:49:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温大哥，还有一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:49:40.92,0:49:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai, there's one thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:43.72,0:49:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}特别法庭指定了一个监护人..
Dialogue: 2,0:49:43.72,0:49:46.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The special court had appointed a custodian...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:47.24,0:49:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道
Dialogue: 2,0:49:47.24,0:49:48.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:49.36,0:49:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们想扣押我们所有的资产
Dialogue: 2,0:49:49.36,0:49:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He wants to attach all our assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:52.52,0:49:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，这是我们所有资产的细节
Dialogue: 2,0:49:52.52,0:49:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. This is the detail of all our assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:56.60,0:49:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和哈萨德得在这上面签字
Dialogue: 2,0:49:56.60,0:49:58.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You and Harshad need to sign this.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:01.16,0:50:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我
Dialogue: 2,0:50:01.16,0:50:02.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Ashwin sighs] - Give.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:02.60,0:50:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我一支笔
Dialogue: 2,0:50:02.60,0:50:03.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give me a pen.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:10.24,0:50:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果法庭下令,
Dialogue: 2,0:50:10.24,0:50:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now if the court has ordered it,
Dialogue: 3,0:50:12.96,0:50:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须附加资产
Dialogue: 2,0:50:12.96,0:50:15.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we will have to attach the assets.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:15.52,0:50:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还有什么选择？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:15.52,0:50:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What option do we have?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:18.28,0:50:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温大哥，至少看一眼吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:18.28,0:50:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Bhai, at least glance at them once?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:21.64,0:50:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你已经看过了，是不是? 那就够了
Dialogue: 2,0:50:21.64,0:50:23.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've seen it, haven't you? That's enough.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:24.72,0:50:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:50:24.72,0:50:25.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:31.68,0:50:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你必须改变你的策略
Dialogue: 2,0:50:31.68,0:50:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have to change your strategy.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:34.56,0:50:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}粉碎他的希望
Dialogue: 2,0:50:34.56,0:50:35.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Crush his hopes.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:36.84,0:50:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他相信如果他不合作..
Dialogue: 2,0:50:36.84,0:50:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Make him believe that if he doesn't co-operate...
Dialogue: 3,0:50:39.48,0:50:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会在监狱里度过余生
Dialogue: 2,0:50:39.48,0:50:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he will rot in custody for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:41.40,0:50:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}照我说的做
Dialogue: 2,0:50:41.40,0:50:43.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Madhavan inhales] - Just do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:44.52,0:50:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道起诉你的案件有多少吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:44.52,0:50:46.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know the number of cases against you?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:47.96,0:50:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}31个
Dialogue: 2,0:50:47.96,0:50:48.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thirty-one.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:50.48,0:50:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欺诈 SBI
Dialogue: 2,0:50:50.48,0:50:51.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Defrauding SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:52.68,0:50:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行汇票贴现案
Dialogue: 2,0:50:52.68,0:50:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}UCO Bank bill discounting case.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:55.56,0:50:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马鲁蒂 · 乌德约格诈骗案
Dialogue: 2,0:50:55.56,0:50:57.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maruti Udyog defrauding case.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:57.68,0:51:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI Cap 诈骗案
Dialogue: 2,0:50:57.68,0:51:00.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI Cap defrauding case.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:01.12,0:51:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也就是说..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:01.12,0:51:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That means...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:03.16,0:51:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你在一个案件中获得保释，就会有第二个
Dialogue: 2,0:51:03.16,0:51:05.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you get bail in one case, there will be a second.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:06.16,0:51:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果第二个给你保释，还会有第三个，以此类推
Dialogue: 2,0:51:06.16,0:51:07.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you get bail in the second case, there will be a third.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:11.28,0:51:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:11.28,0:51:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're going to be so badly b******d...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:13.60,0:51:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再也见不到外面的太阳
Dialogue: 2,0:51:13.60,0:51:15.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you won't be able to stitch your bum back ever.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:21.68,0:51:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了? 蚊子太多了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:21.68,0:51:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'What happened? Too many mosquitoes?'
Dialogue: 3,0:51:26.56,0:51:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便说一下，还有更多的好消息
Dialogue: 2,0:51:26.56,0:51:27.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By the way, there's more good news.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:29.36,0:51:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}执法部门想见你
Dialogue: 2,0:51:29.36,0:51:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Enforcement Directorate wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:32.76,0:51:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[迈达文]“关于一起违反外汇规定的案件”
Dialogue: 2,0:51:32.76,0:51:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Regarding a case of foreign currency violation.'
Dialogue: 3,0:51:37.04,0:51:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也就是说，等我调查完了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:37.04,0:51:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That means, when I'm done...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:39.96,0:51:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们就会开始纠缠你
Dialogue: 2,0:51:39.96,0:51:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they will start badgering you.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:42.20,0:51:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:51:42.20,0:51:42.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it good?
Dialogue: 3,0:51:44.56,0:51:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给他带些驱蚊剂
Dialogue: 2,0:51:44.56,0:51:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bring him some mosquito repellent.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:47.12,0:51:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可能，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:51:47.12,0:51:47.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not possible, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:48.20,0:51:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧，给他点..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:48.20,0:51:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}C'mon, give him some...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:49.72,0:51:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不能，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:51:49.72,0:51:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can't, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:50.72,0:51:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}蚊子会吸光他的血，锁上门
Dialogue: 2,0:51:50.72,0:51:52.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The mosquitoes will suck all his blood. Lock it.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:00.44,0:52:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是哈尔沙德故事的结局..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:00.44,0:52:03.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the end of the Harshad Mehta story...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:03.52,0:52:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如我们所知
Dialogue: 2,0:52:03.52,0:52:04.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...as we know it.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:05.88,0:52:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从贫穷到富有..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:05.88,0:52:07.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}From rags to riches...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:07.96,0:52:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再从富有变成狗
Dialogue: 2,0:52:07.96,0:52:09.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to the dogs.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:16.04,0:52:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么这么严肃，凯迪亚？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:16.04,0:52:17.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why so serious, Kedia?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:18.68,0:52:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托，你们难道不知道..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:18.68,0:52:20.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on. Don't you guys know...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:22.36,0:52:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们和媒体都在追查哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:52:22.36,0:52:24.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...people and the press are after Harshad...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:24.52,0:52:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是 RBI 的调查还在继续
Dialogue: 2,0:52:24.52,0:52:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but RBI's investigation is still on.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:27.64,0:52:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德的被捕意味着迟早..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:27.64,0:52:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Harshad's arrest means, sooner or later...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:30.80,0:52:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会把目光转移到其他人身上
Dialogue: 2,0:52:30.80,0:52:32.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...they will move on to other people.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:33.32,0:52:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 像我们这样的人-得了吧，凯迪亚
Dialogue: 2,0:52:33.32,0:52:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- People like us. - Come on, Kedia.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:36.48,0:52:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里是印度
Dialogue: 2,0:52:36.48,0:52:37.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is India.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:38.36,0:52:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人敢碰这里的外资银行
Dialogue: 2,0:52:38.36,0:52:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No one dares to touch foreign banks here.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:41.04,0:52:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我不经营外资银行
Dialogue: 2,0:52:41.04,0:52:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I don't run a foreign bank.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:44.96,0:52:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:44.96,0:52:45.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:46.32,0:52:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会把你关进监狱吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:46.32,0:52:47.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are they going to put you in jail?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:48.20,0:52:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧，喝酒
Dialogue: 2,0:52:48.20,0:52:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[laughs] -'Come on. Drink up.'
Dialogue: 3,0:52:50.16,0:52:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，不会有事的
Dialogue: 2,0:52:50.16,0:52:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on, Kedia. Nothing is going to happen.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:07.60,0:53:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是从监狱打来的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:07.60,0:53:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm calling from the jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:09.16,0:53:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我别无选择
Dialogue: 2,0:53:09.16,0:53:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I didn't have any other option.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:10.52,0:53:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈沙德，你从监狱打电话给我，是在增加你的麻烦”
Dialogue: 2,0:53:10.52,0:53:14.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Harshad, by calling me from the jail you are increasing your trouble.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:14.48,0:53:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能增加多少？
Dialogue: 2,0:53:14.48,0:53:16.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much can it increase?
Dialogue: 3,0:53:17.04,0:53:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我快死了
Dialogue: 2,0:53:17.04,0:53:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm dying here.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:21.08,0:53:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是我们所有人最后的机会
Dialogue: 2,0:53:21.08,0:53:22.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, this is the last chance for all of us.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:24.20,0:53:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我倒下了，我会把所有人都拖下水
Dialogue: 2,0:53:24.20,0:53:26.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I go down, I'll take everyone down with me.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:26.36,0:53:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会想办法的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:26.36,0:53:27.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I'll do something.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:28.04,0:53:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我得和几个人商量一下
Dialogue: 2,0:53:28.04,0:53:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I'll have to discuss it with a few people.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:30.00,0:53:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没时间了，阁下
Dialogue: 2,0:53:30.00,0:53:31.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no time for that, Swami ji.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:33.16,0:53:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个消息，首相应该..
Dialogue: 2,0:53:33.16,0:53:35.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This message, the Prime Minister should...
Dialogue: 3,0:53:38.00,0:53:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把我的信息直接传达给首相
Dialogue: 2,0:53:38.00,0:53:39.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Convey my message directly to the PM.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:40.92,0:53:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是在威胁这个国家的总理吗
Dialogue: 2,0:53:40.92,0:53:43.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Are you threatening the prime minister of this country?'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:46.52,0:53:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你无所不知，阁下
Dialogue: 2,0:53:46.52,0:53:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are omniscient, Swami ji.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:49.36,0:53:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:53:49.36,0:53:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:58.72,0:54:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧，伙计，把我关起来
Dialogue: 2,0:53:58.72,0:54:00.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come buddy, lock me up.